deactivate DB
AppDB --> BL: List<TransferApplication>
deactivate AppDB

BL --> RestController: List<TransferApplication>
deactivate BL

RestController --> UI: HTTP 200: applications
deactivate RestController

UI --> Staff: Application List with Evaluation Reports
deactivate UI

Staff -> UI: selectCandidates(applicationIds)
activate UI
Staff -> UI: clickForwardToFacultyBoard()

UI -> RestController: PATCH /api/dean/applications/forward-to-faculty (applicationIds)
activate RestController

RestController -> BL: forwardToFacultyBoard(applicationIds)
